{"tha-ap253:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap253:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap253:0.3":"Thomakattheraapadana ","tha-ap253:1.1":"“Devaloke thito santo, ","tha-ap253:1.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap253:1.3":"Dhammam sunitva mudito, ","tha-ap253:1.4":"imam vacam abhasaham. ","tha-ap253:2.1":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap253:2.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","tha-ap253:2.3":"Bahujjanam tarayasi, ","tha-ap253:2.4":"desento amatam padam’. ","tha-ap253:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap253:3.2":"yam vacamabhanim tada; ","tha-ap253:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap253:3.4":"thomanaya idam phalam. ","tha-ap253:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap253:4.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap253:4.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap253:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap253:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma thomako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap253:6.1":"Thomakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}